Kuwa soo uruuriya shaybaarada neefsashada ee bukaanka COVID-19 ama daryeelaya ama gaadiidka u qaada iyagoo aan lahayn nidaam wax soo saar aerosol ah, WHO waxay kugula talineysaa maaskaro qalliinka, indhaha, ama wajiga, dharka ilaalinta iyo gacan.
