Dib u eegis dhaqameed oo horumarineed oo caafimaad ah oo loogu talagalay tallaalka COVID-19 iyo dawada la soo jeediyay ayaa la siiyaa, illaa iyo Abriil 2020. Daawooyin kale oo antivirus ah oo hadda la qiimeeyo daaweynta COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan remdesivir, chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir iyo lopinavir/ritonavir ayaa ku biiray interferon beta.
Waxaa jira caddayn ku saleysan waxtarka remdesivir ilaa iyo bisha Mach 2020.
Kordhinta bukaanka ayaa lagu arkay bukaannada la daaweeyay isticmaalka raxmadda leh ee remdesivir.
Tijaabooyinka Phase III ee caafimaad ee lagu sameeyay Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chloroquine, oo loo isticmaalo daaweynta malariyada ayaa horay loogu bartay Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020, waxay soo bandhigeen natiijooyin horudhac ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waxaa jira baaq dib u eegis ah oo la mid ah cilmi baarista.
Dowladaha Kuuriya iyo Shiinaha waxay ku talinayaan isticmaalka chloroquine.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, Machadka Virology ee Wuhan, halka uu ku talinayo qiyaasta maalinlaha ah ee hal garaam, wuxuu qirayaa in qiyaasta laba-laabadu ay aad u khatar badan tahay oo ay dhimasho keeni karto.
Bishii Maarso 28, 2020, FDA waxay soo saartay oggolaanshaha isticmaalka degdegga ah ee hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine iyadoo la raacayo ikhtiyaarka khabiirada caafimaadka ee daaweynta dadka qaba COVID-19. Tilmaamaha Shiinaha ee daabacaadda 7aad ayaa sidoo kale ku jira interferon, ribavirin ama umifenovir si loo isticmaalo ka hortagga COVID-19.
Xogta hore waxay muujineysaa in qiyaaso sare oo ribavirin ah loo baahan yahay in lagu daaweeyo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitazoxanide waxaa lagu talinayaa in lagu sameeyo daraasado sii kordhaya oo in vivo ah kadib markii la muujiyey heerarka heerarka hoose ee heerarka heerarka sare ee SARS-CoV-2. Daraasaduhu waxay muujinayaan in ku-darka borotiinka horudhaca sare ee serina protease transmembrane 2 (TMPRSS2) ay muhiim u tahay gelitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyada oo loo marayo isdhexgalka la leh ACE2 receptor.
Cilmi-baarista chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo ay weheliso ama aan lahayn azithromycin waxay leedahay xaddidaad weyn oo ka hortageysa bulshada caafimaadka inay isticmaalaan daaweynta iyada oo aan la helin daraasad dheeri ah. Oseltamivir ma soo bandhigto SARS-CoV-2 in vitro mana jirto wax door ah oo la yaqaan daaweynta COVID-19.
Duufaanta cytokine waxay noqon kartaa dhibaatooyin heerka dambe ah oo COVID-19 ah.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in hydroxychloroquine uu leeyahay astaamo anti-sitokin ah. Tocilizumab waxaa lagu daray tilmaamaha daaweynta ee Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha ka dib markii la dhammeystiray daraasad yar.
Waxaa lagu sameeyay tijaabooyin aan kala sooc lahayn oo heer qaran ah oo ku yaal Talyaaniga kadib markii uu helay natiijooyin caafimaad oo caafimaad qaba.
Marka la isku daro baaritaanka dhiigga serum feritine si loo ogaado burburka cytokine, waxaa loola jeedaa in la hortago horumarka, kaas oo loo maleynayo inuu yahay sababta dhimashada dadka qaar ee qaba cudurka.
Interleukin-6 receptor antagonist waxaa ansixiyay FDA iyadoo lagu saleynayo daraasad kiis ah oo dib loo eegay daaweynta cudurka sitokin-deynta ee steroid-ka ee la xiriira sababo kala duwan, CAR-ka T-celinta ee 2017.
Ilaa hadda, ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo si random ah loo xakameeyo in tocilizumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo CRS ah.
U gudbinta unugyada la tallaalay iyo walxaha ay ka soo saaraan nidaamyada difaaca ee ka bogsadaan COVID-19 dadka u baahan ayaa la baaray sidii hab aan tallaal ahayn oo loo tallaalo tallaalka aan la tallaalin.
