Neutralization virus waa habka ficil la filayo ee daaweynta antibody-ka aan la isticmaalin ee noqon karta dhexdhexaadiye difaaca ka dhanka ah SARS-CoV-2.
Habka kale ee loo yaqaan 'cellular cytotoxicity' waa in la ilaaliyaa antibody-ka iyo/ama fagositosis.
Nooc kale oo daaweynta antibody-yada xasaasiga ah, tusaale ahaan, iyadoo la adeegsanayo antibodies monoclonal ah ayaa la horumarinayaa.
Soo saarista serum-ka soo kabashada, oo ka kooban qaybta dhiigga ee bukaanka soo kabsaday oo ku jira unugyo gaar ah oo ku saabsan fayraska ayaa la kordhin karaa si loo fuliyo dhaqso.
